&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.copyblogger.com/&quot;&gt;ProBlogger&lt;/a&gt; (blog, Darren Rowse)&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.guykawasaki.com/books/reality-check.shtml&quot;&gt;Reality Check&lt;/a&gt; (book, Guy Kawasaki)&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1422125009&quot;&gt;Groundswell&lt;/a&gt; (book, Charlene Li)&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.altimetergroup.com/&quot;&gt;The Altimeter&lt;/a&gt; (blog, Charlene Li)&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://shripriya.com/blog/&quot;&gt;Almost as Good as Chocolate&lt;/a&gt; (Shripriya Mahesh)&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.kissmetrics.com/&quot;&gt;KISSmetrics&lt;/a&gt; (blog, &lt;a href=&quot;http://kissmetrics.com/&quot;&gt;KISSmetrics.com&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;

